<Layout title="Donate to Myrient" description="Support Myrient with a donation. Credit card, PayPal, or cryptocurrency.">
  <h1>Donate to Myrient</h1>

  <p>Myrient has grown from a side project to a resource offering organized and publicly available video game collections with the intention of keeping them from becoming lost to time.</p>

  <p>We have never made a profit from Myrient and we continue that commitment to this day by not running advertisements or charging for access.</p>

  <p>Our vision to make video game content available without normal means of monetization is not possible without your support. Your donation will allow us to continue storing over 390 terabytes of data, organizing over 13 million files, and serving over 30 petabytes of content every month.</p>

  <section>
    <h3>Credit/Debit Card, PayPal, Direct Debit, Bank Transfer</h3>
    <p>To donate by card, PayPal, direct debit, or bank transfer, please use the donation widget on the official Myrient site: <a href="https://myrient.erista.me/donate/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">myrient.erista.me/donate/</a>.</p>
  </section>

